#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.jv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.jv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:1 of
msgid "Bessel function of the first kind of real order and complex argument."
msgstr "实数阶、复数参数的第一类贝塞尔函数。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.jv.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:3 of
msgid "Order (float)."
msgstr "阶数（浮点数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:5 of
msgid "Argument (float or complex)."
msgstr "参数（浮点数或复数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:7 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "可选的输出数组，用于存储函数值"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.jv.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:10 of
msgid "**J** -- Value of the Bessel function, :math:`J_v(z)`."
msgstr "**J** -- 贝塞尔函数的值，:math:`J_v(z)`。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.jv.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:15 of
msgid ":py:obj:`jve`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:16 of
msgid ":math:`J_v` with leading exponential behavior stripped off."
msgstr "去除了主导指数行为的 :math:`J_v`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`spherical_jn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:19 of
msgid "spherical Bessel functions."
msgstr "球贝塞尔函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`j0`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:22 of
msgid "faster version of this function for order 0."
msgstr "阶数为 0 时该函数的快速版本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`j1`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:25 of
msgid "faster version of this function for order 1."
msgstr "阶数为 1 时该函数的快速版本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:28 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:29 of
msgid ""
"For positive `v` values, the computation is carried out using the AMOS "
"[1]_ `zbesj` routine, which exploits the connection to the modified "
"Bessel function :math:`I_v`,"
msgstr ""
"对于正的 `v` 值，使用 AMOS [1]_ 的 `zbesj` 例程进行计算，该例程利用了与"
"修正贝塞尔函数 :math:`I_v` 的关系，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:33 of
msgid ""
"J_v(z) = \\exp(v\\pi\\imath/2) I_v(-\\imath z)\\qquad (\\Im z > 0)\n"
"\n"
"J_v(z) = \\exp(-v\\pi\\imath/2) I_v(\\imath z)\\qquad (\\Im z < 0)"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:38 of
msgid "For negative `v` values the formula,"
msgstr "对于负的 `v` 值，使用公式，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:40 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"J_{-v}(z) = J_v(z) \\cos(\\pi v) - Y_v(z) \\sin(\\pi v)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:42 of
msgid ""
"is used, where :math:`Y_v(z)` is the Bessel function of the second kind, "
"computed using the AMOS routine `zbesy`.  Note that the second term is "
"exactly zero for integer `v`; to improve accuracy the second term is "
"explicitly omitted for `v` values such that `v = floor(v)`."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`Y_v(z)` 是第二类贝塞尔函数，使用 AMOS 的 `zbesy` 例程计算。"
"注意到当 `v` 为整数时第二项恰好为零；为了提高精度，对于满足 `v = floor(v)"
"` 的 `v` 值，第二项被显式省略。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:47 of
msgid ""
"Not to be confused with the spherical Bessel functions (see "
"`spherical_jn`)."
msgstr "不要与球贝塞尔函数（见 `spherical_jn`）混淆。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:50 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.jv:51 of
msgid ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, A Portable Package for Bessel Functions of a "
"Complex Argument and Nonnegative Order\", http://netlib.org/amos/"
msgstr ""

